{
  "stem": "25809.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You-- I know I couldn't go outside because the Germans would pick me up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I was-- I would be walking by myself, they might-- somebody might stop me and say, hey, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was curfew at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At 10:00, nobody could be out on the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- I still don't remember how I got through it, except I know one of the things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whenever I am in a condominium, or in an apartment, I can't wait to get out of the place, because I feel so claustrophobic.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- it just drives me bananas to be in small spaces, because I was literally closed up in this small area-- nothing to do except maybe some reading.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could listen to some radio, which became boring after a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because yeah, you listen to a radio and you can still do other things, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you brought-- you had books there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had some books, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing that kept me going-- that seemed to keep me going at night is that I had always music going through my head, and I would go to bed maybe at 8:30, 9:00 and I would lay in bed, and I would think about music and all kinds of musical-- I had asked my father when I was-- I was eight years old.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when the war-- about that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said I would like-- we were living right behind the conservatory, in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had asked my father if I could go to the conservatory instead of going to school.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
